snippet.textDisplay: I actually have a story about my experience with the conspiracy collection. I was looking forward to getting on, but I had a class. Of course, the only logical thing to do was to look at my schedule and see if there was any way I could be a bit late to my class at 10 am (I live in Los Angeles). Miraculously I had P.E. and a snack break before. So my plan was to get changed during my nutrition and have the Jeffree Star Cosmetics sight up to be ready right when the changing time begins ( at ten). I had it ready with my account already set up. I didn't know what I wanted but I was willing to get anything I could manage to put in my cart. When it was ten I frantically added the lip balm and lipstick into my cart. The site crashed and I was crushed. Throughout the period by one of my friends would say they were going to the restroom but in reality, we were reloading the page. We sadly didn't get anything in the collection, but I am looking forward to the next launch!
